	<title>Introduction</title>

	<caution>
		<para>This extension in alpha state.</para>
		<para>
			The current version is only compatible with <productname>TYPO3</productname> 4.5 LTS
			and the corresponding version of <productname>extbase</productname> (1.3). <sbr />
			There is a version for <productname>TYPO3</productname> 4.4 and <productname>extbase</productname> 1.2 on
			github in the <literal>extbase-1.2</literal> branch. But this is deprecated, so don't expect any bugfixes
			or even new features.
		</para>
	</caution>
	
	<section xml:id="chapter.introduction.whatdoesitdo">
		<title>What does it do?</title>
		<para>
			This extension provides a simple calendar.
		</para>
	</section>
	
	<section xml:id="chapter.introduction.features">
		<title>Feature List</title>
		<itemizedlist>
			<listitem><simpara>Allday Events</simpara></listitem>
			<listitem><simpara>Recurring Events</simpara></listitem>
			<listitem><simpara>Exceptions, Exception Groups</simpara></listitem>
			<listitem><simpara>Categories</simpara></listitem>
			<listitem><simpara>adding actions via Typoscript</simpara></listitem>
			<listitem><simpara>templates using the hCalendar and hCard microformats</simpara></listitem>
			<listitem><simpara>...and all the goodness that is <productname>Extbase</productname> and <productname>Fluid</productname>.</simpara></listitem>
		</itemizedlist>
	</section>
	
